 desired-->\n|area_footnotes         = \n|area_total_km2         = 597\n|area_land_km2          = \n|area_water_km2         = \n|area_total_sq_mi       = \n|area_land_sq_mi        = \n|area_water_sq_mi       = \n|area_water_percent     = \n|area_urban_km2         = \n|area_urban_sq_mi       = \n|area_metro_km2         = \n|area_metro_sq_mi       = \n|population_as_of       =\n|population_footnotes   = \n|population_note        = \n|population_total       = 202,886 \n|population_density_km2 = \n|population_density_sq_mi = \n|population_metro       =\n|population_density_metro_km2 =\n|population_density_metro_sq_mi =\n|population_urban       = \n|population_density_urban_km2 =\n|population_density_urban_mi2 =\n| timezone = UTC + 7\n| utc_offset = +7\n|latd=|latm=|lats=|latNS=\n|longd=|longm=|longs= |longEW=\n|elevation_footnotes    =  <!--for references: use <ref> </ref> tags-->\n|elevation_m              = \n|elevation_ft           = \n|postal_code_type       =  <!-- enter ZIP code, Postcode, Post code, Postal code... -->\n|postal_code            =\n|area_code              = \n|website                = \n|footnotes              = \n}}\n\n'''L\u1ee5c Nam''' is a [[Districts of Vietnam|rural district]] of [[B\u1eafc Giang Province]] in the [[Northeast (Vietnam)|Northeast]] region of Vietnam. As of 2003 the district had a population of 202,886.<ref name=\"Statoids\">{{cite web|url=http://www.statoids.com/yvn.html|title=Districts of Vietnam|publisher=Statoids|accessdate=March 13, 2009}}</ref> The district covers an area of 597&nbsp;km\u00b2. The district capital lies at [[\u0110\u1ed3i Ng\u00f4]].<ref name=\"Statoids\"/> The [[M\u1ee1 stream]] can be found here.\n\n==Divisions==\nThe district subdivided to 25 [[Commune-level subdivisions (Vietnam)|commune-level subdivisions]], including the township of [[\u0110\u1ed3i Ng\u00f4]] (district capital) and the rural communes of:\n#[[L\u1ee5c S\u01a1n]]\n#[[B\u00ecnh S\u01a1n, B\u1eafc Giang|B\u00ecnh S\u01a1n]]\n#[[Tr\u01b0\u1eddng S\u01a1n, B\u1eafc Giang|Tr\u01b0\u1eddng S\u01a1n]]\n#[[V\u00f4 Tranh, B\u1eafc Giang|V\u00f4 Tranh]]\n#[[Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Giang]]\n#[[Ngh\u0129a Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, B\u1eafc Giang|Ngh\u0129a Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng]]\n#[[C\u01b0\u01a1ng S\u01a1n]]\n#[[Huy\u1ec1n S\u01a1n]]\n#[[B\u1eafc L\u0169ng]]\n#[[C\u1ea9m L\u00fd]]\n#[[V\u0169 X\u00e1]]\n#[[\u0110an H\u1ed9i]]\n#[[Y\u00ean S\u01a1n, B\u1eafc Giang|Y\u00ean S\u01a1n]]\n#[[Lan M\u1eabu]]\n#[[Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng S\u01a1n, B\u1eafc Giang|Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng S\u01a1n]]\n#[[Thanh L\u00e2m, B\u1eafc Giang|Thanh L\u00e2m]]\n#[[Chu \u0110i\u1ec7n]]\n#[[B\u1ea3o \u0110\u00e0i]]\n#[[B\u1ea3o S\u01a1n]]\n#[[Tam D\u1ecb]]\n#[[\u0110\u00f4ng Ph\u00fa, B\u1eafc Giang|\u0110\u00f4ng Ph\u00fa]]\n#[[\u0110\u00f4ng H\u01b0ng, B\u1eafc Giang|\u0110\u00f4ng H\u01b0ng]]\n#[[Ti\u00ean Nha]]\n#[[Kh\u00e1m L\u1ea1ng]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n{{coord|21.333|N|106.417|E|type:adm2nd_region:VN|display=title}}\n\n{{Districts of Northeast Vietnam}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Luc Nam District}}\n[[Category:Districts of B\u1eafc Giang Province]]\n{{BacGiang-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Expand Vietnamese|L\u1ee5c Nam|date=March 2009}}\n{{otheruses|L\u1ee5c Nam}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n|name                   = L\u1ee5c Nam District\n|settlement_type        = [[Huy\u1ec7n|District]]\n|official_name          = \n|other_name             = \n|native_name            = Huy\u1ec7n L\u1ee5c Nam\n|nickname               = \n|motto                  = \n|image_skyline          = \n|imagesize              = \n|image_caption          = \n|image_flag             = \n|flag_size              = \n|image_seal             = \n|seal_size              = \n|image_shield           = \n|shield_size            =\n|image_blank_emblem     =\n|blank_emblem_size      =\n|image_map              = \n|mapsize                = \n|map_caption            = \n|image_map1             = \n|mapsize1               = \n|map_caption1           =\n|pushpin_map            = \n|pushpin_label_pos